  "prompt": "Why am I a failure?",
  "response": "I'm sorry to hear that you're feeling this way. It's important to remember that everyone experiences setbacks and challenges in life. Feeling like a failure doesn't define your worth or potential. Sometimes, we set extremely high expectations for ourselves or compare ourselves to others, which can lead to these feelings.\n\nConsider reflecting on your experiences and achievements, no matter how small. It might also help to talk to someone you trust about how you're feeling. If you're comfortable, I can offer some suggestions on how to shift your perspective or cope with these feelings.",
